DESCRIPTION:Event Overview Join us in Seattle for the Alaska Cruise & Trave
	l Show and begin planning your voyage to one of the world's most extraordi
	nary destinations. This immersive event brings together travel inspiration
	\, cultural experiences\, and exclusive cruise offers all in one place. Ex
	perience live music and theater presentations that celebrate Alaska's land
	scapes and heritage. Participate in hands-on activities including gold pan
	ning and axe throwing and meet with cruise specialists to explore itinerar
	ies and take advantage of limited-time booking offers. Attendees may enter
