UID:_KdJpEt63SPJeV8EkXs5_
SUMMARY:Women's Conference
DTSTAMP:20260319T022249Z
DTSTART:20260321T160000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a day centered on Jesus\, our wonderful counselor. 
	We’ll hear from Kacey Batterton\, a licensed counselor\, sharing how the c
	are Jesus modeled in scripture is echoed in how counselors are taught to c
	are for others. Together\, we’ll explore what Christlike empathy\, listeni
	ng\, and compassion can look like for all of us. Not as experts\, but as w
	omen learning to love well. This is a free\, one-day event open to women o
	f all ages \\(teens 13\\+ welcome\\). Bring a friend\, everyone is invited
	! Lunch isn’t included\, but we’ll have a room reserved at a local restaur
	ant for anyone who’d like to gather during the break. Come as you are. Be 
	encouraged\, equipped\, and reminded of the gentle care of Jesus.\n\nhttps
	://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/women-s-conference/18291026/2026-
