BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:YClIIQ2igJ3yfay8PHsil
SUMMARY:AMBASSADOR COMMITTEE MEETING
DTSTAMP:20260319T022250Z
DTSTART:20260401T150000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Ambassador Committee meeting is a key gathering for Chamber
	 ambassadors to connect\, collaborate\, and plan initiatives that foster p
	ositive relationships between the Greater Issaquah Chamber of Commerce and
