SUMMARY:Business Impact NW Drop Ins
DTSTAMP:20260319T022250Z
DTSTART:20260401T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Description Join us at the Kent Chamber of Commerce for free\, 
	in-person business support from Business Impact NW. Whether you?re launchi
	ng a new venture or growing an existing one\, drop in to get one-on-one gu
	idance on business planning\, funding options\, certifications\, and more.
	 No appointment necessary?just bring your questions and your goals! Schedu
	le time here - Calendly\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/b
